<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{title}} - Deno App</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/static/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <nav id="main-nav">
      <a href="/" class="brand-logo" id="brand-logo">
        <span class="brand-icon"></span>
        <span class="brand-text">AGILE</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/about" id="nav-about">About</a>
      <div class="dropdown">
        <a href="#" class="dropbtn" id="nav-resources">Resources ▼</a>
        <div class="dropdown-content">
          <a href="/resources/documentation" id="nav-resources-docs">Documentation</a>
          <a href="/resources/tutorials" id="nav-resources-tutorials">Tutorials</a>
          <a href="/resources/support" id="nav-resources-support">Support</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {{#if isAdmin}}
        <a href="/admin/users" id="nav-admin-users">Users</a>
        <a href="/admin/roles" id="nav-admin-roles">Roles</a>
      {{/if}}
      {{#if isLoggedIn}}
        <a href="/logout" class="nav-right" id="nav-logout">Logout</a>
      {{else}}
        <a href="/login" class="nav-right" id="nav-login">Login</a>
      {{/if}}
    </nav>
    
    {{#if isLoggedIn}}
      <div class="user-info" id="user-info-display">Logged in as: {{user.email}}</div>
    {{/if}}
    
    <h1 id="page-title">{{title}}</h1>
    
    <div class="content-section">
      <h2>Step-by-Step Tutorials</h2>
      <p>Learn how to use the application with these hands-on tutorials.</p>
      
      <div class="tutorial-card">
        <h3>Tutorial 1: Creating Your First User</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Log in as admin (admin@example.com / admin123)</li>
          <li>Navigate to Users in the admin menu</li>
          <li>Fill in the user details (email, name, password)</li>
          <li>Select appropriate roles using checkboxes</li>
          <li>Click "Create User" button</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="tutorial-time">⏱️ Estimated time: 2 minutes</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tutorial-card">
        <h3>Tutorial 2: Managing Roles</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Navigate to Roles in the admin menu</li>
          <li>Create a new role with a descriptive name</li>
          <li>Add a clear description of the role's purpose</li>
          <li>Assign the role to users in the Users section</li>
          <li>Edit or delete roles as needed</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="tutorial-time">⏱️ Estimated time: 3 minutes</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tutorial-card">
        <h3>Tutorial 3: Running Selenium Tests</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Ensure the application is running on localhost:8000</li>
          <li>Open a terminal and run: <code>deno task test</code></li>
          <li>Watch as automated tests verify functionality</li>
          <li>Review test results and screenshots if needed</li>
          <li>Run specific test suites with test:auth, test:users, etc.</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="tutorial-time">⏱️ Estimated time: 5 minutes</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="tutorial-card">
        <h3>Tutorial 4: Password Migration</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Run the migration script: <code>deno task migrate-passwords</code></li>
          <li>All plain text passwords will be converted to bcrypt</li>
          <li>Verify users can still log in with their passwords</li>
          <li>New passwords are automatically hashed on creation</li>
        </ol>
        <p class="tutorial-time">⏱️ Estimated time: 2 minutes</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
